==Etymology==
The [[Sundocarme|Root]]s for "two" have been [[AT]]-AT, AT[[TA]] and other variants. The [[Common Eldarin]] ancestor was ''[[at치ta]]''. 

According to the legend of ''[[Cuivienyarna]]'', the word perhaps derives from the name [[Tata]].<ref>{{WJ|Quendi}}, p. 421</ref>
